25683465.review:
Great game for early access, really fun engaging gameplay.

A few good things that caught my eye so far:
- awesome mix of RTS and space combat;
- exciting dogfights;
- the score and sound design set a great atmosphere;
- ship and station models are beautifully crafted;
- plenty of upgrades to tweak your personal fleet;
- highly customizable controls;
- much to do and much more to come with development;
- great dev;
- runs smooth as silk for me, not a single crash so far.

Yup, off to build my space empire.... hopefully the wife will understand my absence
